race.description: Ladbrokes Bet Ticker Dogs Only Ht 1
race.comment: CASH THE DENNIS (2) won by 0.8 lengths last start when getting around this track 324m in a head turning 17.48. In winning form and can measure up again. BOOM BOOM BUDDY (8) doesn't win out of turn. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing third (18.04) at this track. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Expected to be in the finish again. MIGHTY LAD (7) has a strong overall record having nine wins and 19 places from 38 starts including a last start second (17.89) over 324m at this track. Goes well from this draw. Meets a moderate line up and should run well. DESPICABLE KYRO (4) is worth consideration after filling a hole from the same draw last start.
